t: "Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Wata yimЙ“e jalnor yimЙ“e : hino gasa hara Й“en (jalaaЙ“e) hino Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude. Wanaa rewЙ“e woni ko jalnorta rewЙ“e : hino gasa hara Й“en no Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude. Wata on aybidnir ko'e-mon, wata on bugondir jammooje (bonЙ—e). Innde faasiqaaku nden bonii Й“aawo nde gomЙ—inal nden. Kala mo tuubaali, ko Й“en woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"